# AI Workforce Navigator - Product Requirements Document

## Product Overview
AI-driven SaaS platform integrated with Galileo Search for HR managers to plan and execute AI workforce transformations.

## Target Users
- HR Managers
- Recruitment Consultants
- Business Development Teams
- Department Heads

## Core Features & Requirements

### 1. Assessment Wizard
- Company profile analysis
- Team assessment
- AI readiness evaluation
- Step-by-step guided flow
- Progress saving capability

### 2. Use Case Generator
- Industry-specific AI solutions
- ROI calculations
- Implementation complexity scoring
- Competitor examples
- Cost-benefit analysis

### 3. Job Description Generator
- AI role templates
- Customization options
- Downloadable formats
- Integration with recruitment workflow
- Skill requirement mapping

### 4. Implementation Planning
- Timeline generation
- Resource allocation
- Cost projections
- Risk assessment
- Training recommendations

## Technical Requirements

### Frontend
- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript
- ShadCN@latest components
- Dark mode by default
- Responsive design

### Backend
- Supabase integration
- Authentication system
- Data persistence
- API security
- Performance optimization

### State Management
- Zustand stores
- Type-safe implementations
- Clear data flow
- Persistent storage where needed

## Success Metrics
- User completion rate
- Assessment accuracy
- Implementation success
- Lead generation
- Client engagement

